6  PLANNED CHANGES TO IMPROVE SAFETY



Valero is continuously investigating and reviewing technology and/or applications that could possibly enhance its safety efforts.  These currently include:



-    Fire Water System Upgrade;

-    Relocating EIV actuation panels to main roads or outside process battery limits;

-    Burner Management System upgrades on fired heaters;

-    Placement of additional hydro-foaming stations in high LPG areas;

-    Electronic Safe Work Permitting System; and,

-    New Maintenance and Firehouse Complex outside refiner fence line.
